    { question: "BIOS aur UEFI ka main kaam kya hai?", options: ["Virus scan karna", "Computer ke hardware ko initialize karna aur OS load karna", "Internet connection establish karna", "RAM ko clean karna"], correctIndex: 1, explanation: "BIOS/UEFI firmware hai jo computer on hone pe hardware check karta hai (POST) aur phir OS ko load karta hai. Firmware attack dangerous hota hai kyunki OS se bhi pehle chalti hai." },
