  "cb-08": [
    { question: "Metasploitable 2 kya hai aur lab mein kyun use hota hai?", options: ["Metasploit ka updated version", "Deliberately vulnerable Linux VM — practice ke liye intentionally insecure target", "Kali Linux ka alternative", "Firewall software"], correctIndex: 1, explanation: "Metasploitable 2 = intentionally vulnerable Linux machine hai jo practice ke liye banayi gayi hai. Isme 50+ known vulnerabilities hain — UnrealIRCd backdoor, vsftpd backdoor, Samba exploit, DVWA etc. Safe environment mein attacks practice karne ke liye perfect target." },
